Length: 43
Word count: 6
Reverse:  elpmaxE snoitcnuF gnirtS PHP !dlroW olleH 
Position of 'World': 7
Replace 'World' with 'Universe':  Hello Universe! PHP String Functions Example 
Lowercase:  hello world! php string functions example 
Uppercase:  HELLO WORLD! PHP STRING FUNCTIONS EXAMPLE 
Ucfirst: Hello World! PHP String Functions Example
Repeat: PHP PHP PHP 
Substring (0-5):  Hell
Compare 'Hello' and 'World': -1


